  <description type="morphology">Plants terrestrial or subaquatic, annual. Stems decumbent or erect, greenish red in
        age, diffusely branched, to 10 cm. Leaf blades narrow-lanceolate, 1.5–3 mm, apex obtuse.
        Inflorescences lax; flowers 1 per node. Pedicels 0.5–3 mm. Flowers 4-merous; sepals
        triangular-ovate, 0.4–0.6 mm, apex obtuse; petals ovate, 1.3–1.5 mm. Follicles ascending,
        9–15-seeded, oblong; old follicles spreading, flat. Seeds oblong to ellipsoid, 0.2–0.4(–0.5)
        × 0.1–0.3 mm, prickly-papillate, dull, smooth.</description>
